<plot>A mother must attend a wake in Williamsburg, Brooklyn. Unable to find a sitter for her three children, she has no choice but to bring them along. The funeral Director suggests the children will be better off downstairs in the lounge. When the widow Pepisino asks for the Ladies room she is directed downstairs to the lounge where, unfortunately, she encounters the children "playing" in the casket display room. She mistakes them for something quite different. Chaos ensues and the mother must hustle her brood out.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?412277</url></doc>
